            <head rendition="simple:right">TUESDAY, APRIL 10.<lb/>
            </head>

            <p>After the Journals were read, the House<lb/>adjourned until half-past two to-morrow,<lb/>at the request of <persName ref="pers:SMIT1">Hon. Mr. Smith</persName>, who<lb/>stated that the Government had tendered<lb/>their resignations to His Excellency, but<lb/>the acceptance had not been received or<lb/>the correspondence closed.</p>

<p rendition="simple:right">T. P. D.<lb/>
            </p>

